@startuml
title 分布式锁状态、阶段、Provider 结果关系图

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

enum LockStatus <<CODE: API Final Status>> {
  ACQUIRED
  SUCCESS
  NOT_ACQUIRED
  EXECUTION_FAILED
  LOCK_LOST
  FENCING_REJECTED
  RELEASE_FAILED
  PROVIDER_ERROR
  INVALID_OPTIONS
}

enum LockStage <<CODE: API Stage>> {
  VALIDATE
  ACQUIRE
  WAIT
  EXECUTE
  FENCING
  RENEW
  RELEASE
  CHECK
}

enum LockAcquireStatus <<CODE: Provider Acquire Status>> {
  ACQUIRED
  NOT_ACQUIRED
  PROVIDER_ERROR
}

enum LockRenewStatus <<CODE: Provider Renew Status>> {
  RENEWED
  NOT_FOUND
  NOT_OWNER
  PROVIDER_ERROR
}

enum LockReleaseStatus <<CODE: Provider Release Status>> {
  RELEASED
  NOT_FOUND
  NOT_OWNER
  PROVIDER_ERROR
}

enum LockCheckStatus <<CODE: Provider Check Status>> {
  HELD
  NOT_FOUND
  NOT_OWNER
  PROVIDER_ERROR
}

class LockResult <<CODE: API Result>> {
  - LockStatus status
  - LockStage stage
  - boolean acquired
  - T value
  - LockHandle handle
  - Throwable error
}

class LockEvent <<CODE: Core Event>> {
  - LockEventType eventType
  - LockStage stage
  - LockStatus status
  - Throwable error
}

LockResult --> LockStatus : final result
LockResult --> LockStage : occurred at

LockEvent --> LockStatus : current/final status
LockEvent --> LockStage : event stage

LockAcquireStatus ..> LockStatus : ACQUIRED => ACQUIRED\nNOT_ACQUIRED => NOT_ACQUIRED\nPROVIDER_ERROR => PROVIDER_ERROR
LockAcquireStatus ..> LockStage : mapped stage = ACQUIRE or WAIT

LockRenewStatus ..> LockStatus : NOT_FOUND / NOT_OWNER => LOCK_LOST\nPROVIDER_ERROR => PROVIDER_ERROR
LockRenewStatus ..> LockStage : mapped stage = RENEW

LockReleaseStatus ..> LockStatus : PROVIDER_ERROR => RELEASE_FAILED\nNOT_FOUND / NOT_OWNER => LOCK_LOST or SUCCESS + event
LockReleaseStatus ..> LockStage : mapped stage = RELEASE

LockCheckStatus ..> LockStatus : NOT_FOUND / NOT_OWNER => LOCK_LOST\nPROVIDER_ERROR => PROVIDER_ERROR
LockCheckStatus ..> LockStage : mapped stage = CHECK

note right of LockStatus
  LockStatus 表示最终结果。
  它不表达错误发生在哪一步。
end note

note right of LockStage
  LockStage 表示生命周期阶段。
  它和 LockStatus 组合使用。
end note

note bottom of LockRenewStatus
  ProviderStatus 是底层事实。
  Core 层负责把它映射成：
  LockStatus + LockStage + RuntimeFlag。
end note

@enduml